The Colbert Report - Monday, August 4, 2014 (WEBRip - MP4)
----------------------------------------------------------

The prince of punditry Stephen Colbert is here, winning every one-sided

they deserve. Watch him making "Dead to Me" judgments or showing guests how
sadly misinformed they are (take that, Anderson Cooper and George Lucas).
Brash and unapologetic, the Peabody Award-winning The Colbert Report is
state of the news commentary, with the passion of a religious revival,
and the subtly of a pro-wrestling throw down.

Produced by Comedy Central.

Pat Buchanan and John Dean offer first-hand accounts of the Watergate scandal.
